&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Interrogate briefs with strategy and client management, reframing challenges to unlock distinctive creative opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead the creative platform on your projects, architecting scalable systems that work coherently across all touchpoints, including web, mobile, social, physical retail, packaging, events and emerging channels.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and frame potential iconic moves, testing feasibility with delivery and challenging the team to think bigger. Consider how the ideas can travel across contexts to better resonate with the audience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build senior relationships with clients and partners, leading co-creation sessions that shape decisions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop your team, coaching individuals towards their potential and creating space for originality to emerge. Encourage them to think across channels and think about the whole consumer journey

